definition.en: Person(s) who wrote the music [for lyricist, use “lyrics by” (P676)]. The person or organization who wrote a composition, or who is the composer of a work performed at some event.
definition.de: Künstler, der musikalische Werke schafft. The person or organization who wrote a composition, or who is the composer of a work performed at some event.
definition.fr: Auteur de la musique. The person or organization who wrote a composition, or who is the composer of a work performed at some event.
definition.es: Persona encargada de escribir la música de una obra musical. The person or organization who wrote a composition, or who is the composer of a work performed at some event.
